Feed the Linux kernel with a hwrng
----------------------------------

This is a packaging of rng-tools which runs rngd.

Usage:

 $ docker run --cap-add SYS_ADMIN --device /dev/hwrng:/dev/hwrng:rw ewindisch/rngd

Usage (ARM):

 $ docker run --cap-add SYS_ADMIN --device /dev/hwrng:/dev/hwrng:rw ewindisch/armhf-rpi-rngd
